      <title>Jethmalani：预计印度将在二月份首次降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-23/jethmalani-expect-india-s-first-rate-cut-in-february-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管印度经济增长依然疲软，食品价格波动导致通胀率居高不下，印度储备银行 12 月初仍将基准利率维持在 6.5% 不变。RBL 银行经济学家 Achala Jethmalani 在接受彭博社《中东和非洲视野》主播 Joumanna Bercetche 采访时解释说，预计明年将降息。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-23/jethmalani-expect-india-s-first-rate-cut-in-february-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 06:05:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
